import React from 'react';
import { TextField, Button, Box, Typography } from '@mui/material';

const Register = () => {
  const handleSubmit = (event) => {
    event.preventDefault();
    // handle form logic here
  };

  return (
    <Box className="container" maxWidth="sm" mx="auto" mt={5}>
      <Typography variant="h4" align="center" gutterBottom>
        Register
      </Typography>

      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} noValidate>
        <Box my={2}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            required
            id="email"
            label="Email"
            name="email"
            type="email"
            variant="outlined"
          />
        </Box>

        <Box my={2}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            id="first_name"
            label="First Name"
            name="first_name"
            type="text"
            variant="outlined"
          />
        </Box>

        <Box my={2}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            id="last_name"
            label="Last Name"
            name="last_name"
            type="text"
            variant="outlined"
          />
        </Box>

        <Box my={2}>
          <TextField
            fullWidth
            required
            id="password"
            label="Password"
            name="password"
            type="password"
            variant="outlined"
          />
        </Box>

        <Box mt={3} textAlign="center">
          <Button variant="contained" color="primary" type="submit">
            Submit
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </form>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
